description.content:
Hello! I am Faisal. I am a Software Engineer and grip on Web Development. I will follow best practices of web engineering to make efficient web app.


I have experience of years in web development, specially of PHP and Laravel. I am full stack developer and know both frontend and backend. Also, I have done projects for industry. So, if there are any issue in existing site or want a brand new site according to your need, I am here for you.


What will I do?


  • Make new web apps
  • Will resolve backend and frontend issues
  • Deployment/installation
  • Upgrade Features
  • Upgrade Laravel Version
  • RESTful APIs development and integration
  • Payment gateways integration
  • Efficient Database
  • Working according to Software Engineering Knowledge


I will work using following technologies

  • Laravel
  • HTML, CSS, JS, jQuery, Bootstrap
  • MySQL database


Note: Time and Prices can vary depends on size of project.


Kindly inbox me before placing order.


I am here for you to work according to your requirements and satisfaction. :)


#Laravel Developer #Ecommerce #Frontend # Backend #Bug_fixing #Upgradation
